title: Girls Choir Wows Audience With Their Spin On ‘Bohemian Rhapsody’
text:
Girls Choir Wows Audience With Their Spin On ‘Bohemian Rhapsody’ Subscribe to Reshareworthy! It's FREE and always will be! 
During a school choral festival, the girls choir group Frensham Madrigals give an amazing performance of the classic Queen song “”Bohemian Rhapsody”. The talented girls impressed the audience and judges with their take on one of Queen’s most popular songs. The Australian youth choral group has won a number of competitions and you’re about to hear one of the reasons why they are so celebrated.
